===Usage===
There are two variations on the stressed syllable in the genitive case.  Generally, both variations are applicable.  However, when used in the expressions [[#Idioms |ни хуя́]] (ni khuyá) и [[#Idioms|до хуя́]] (do khuyá), the last syllable should be stressed.

